{
  "stem": "25651.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I saw her for the first time in 1990, there's this old woman comes to me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, I'm an old man, but there's this old woman comes to me, and says, Micha, Micha, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Where have you been all my life?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So, I was supposed to run to the Seidels.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So, I knew that there was an underground type of activity.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I knew that there was something going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I was a kid, and what I wasn't told, I was not supposed to know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] In the summer of 1943, we'd been there nearly a year, my sister-in-law, [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Traute, ?] was working in a factory that was making bindings for the German army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And because of that, she got extra rations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now, how did we get other extra rations?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because Milos got a job in a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So Milos would steal food from the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I would be the means of carrying it to [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Traute, ?] who would somehow get it cooked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the best meal that we kids had, in the [INAUDIBLE], was buchty [SPEAKING CZECH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm saying it in Czech, because we always laugh when we talk about this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a sort of cake, which was made out of-- it was a roll, but it was soft dough.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a cakey type of thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Bit of sugar in it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was sweet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on top of it was a sauce, which was made out of coffee and margarine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the margarine wasn't dissolved in it, but somehow-- it wasn't emulsified.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, they didn't have mixers and things-- the little bits of margarine would float in this sauce like yellow dots.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was actually quite pretty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You're making a face.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
